  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Frank Reed, |. w. w. leader, is\nto be tried in Justice Suckers\ncourt on two charges-conspiracy\nand flag dissertation. Changes of\nvenue were made this morning\ntransferring the cases from the jur-\nisdiction of the police court.\n\n\nChief of Police Sullivan swore to\nthe complaint charging Reed with\nconspiracy, while Captain of Detec-\ntives Burns charged Reed with des-\necrating the Stars and Stripes.\n\n\nReed was arrested in the |. w.\nw. hall for speaking disrespectfully\nof the American flag."
    }
  ]
